Privacy Policy

TextPadPro respects your privacy.

Data Collection
TextPadPro does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.
The app does not use analytics, tracking, advertising frameworks, or third-party SDKs.

Local Processing
All text snippets and settings are stored locally on your device.
TextPadPro does not upload user content to external servers.

Network Communication
TextPadPro may accept local network connections (Bonjour/TCP) from its companion
iOS/iPadOS app, TextPadRemote, to enable remote editing and paste functionality.
All communication occurs on the local network only and is not transmitted over the internet.

Accessibility
TextPadPro requires macOS Accessibility permission solely to paste text into the
frontmost application at the user’s request.

Third Parties
TextPadPro does not share data with third parties.

Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:

Email: keith@YOURDOMAIN.com

